## RedemptionDetails.actualONEUAmount property

Amount of ONEU that was actually redeemed by the transaction.

**Signature:**

```typescript
actualONEUAmount: Decimal;
```

## Remarks

This can end up being lower than `attemptedONEUAmount` due to interference from another transaction that modifies the list of Troves.
